l-koch-aspen-estate-sign-colorado-record-setting-real-estate-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740217622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a531f5bfebcc4d029e2102%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-koch-aspen-estate-sign-colorado-record-setting-real-estate-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20Koch%20brothers%20has%20relisted%20his%20Aspen%20estate%20for%20its%20highest-ever%20price%3A%20%24125%20million.%20It%20could%20break%20a%20state%20record%20set%20just%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-koch-aspen-estate-sign-colorado-record-setting-real-estate-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajra%20Roti%2C%20Garlic%20Chutney%3A%20Protesting%20Rajasthan%20MLAs'%20Buffet%20At%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20Congress%20leaders%20continued%20their%20protest%2C%20two%20men%20carrying%20large%20tiffin%20boxes%20walked%20up%20the%20stairs%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20to%20feed%20the%20hungry%20MLAs.%20Inside%20the%20tiffin%20boxes%20were%20chapatis%20made%20from%20Bajra%2C%20%3Cem%3Egatte%20ki%20sabzi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20garlic%20chutney%2C%20%3Cem%3Edum%20aloo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Efogla%20raita%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eamong%20other%20dishes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20stem%20from%20a%20BJP%20leader's%20remarks%20on%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20during%20question%20hour%20of%20the%20assembly%20yesterday.%20After%20a%20sleepover%20inside%20the%20premises%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20decided%20to%20fuel%20their%20resistance%20with%20a%20home-cooked%20feast.%20Congress%20MLA%20Anil%20Sharma%20took%20charge%20of%20catering%20duties%2C%20bringing%20food%20from%20his%20own%20kitchen.%20Mr%20Sharma's%20gesture%20follows%20a%20practice%20upheld%20by%20his%20family.%20His%20father%2C%20Bhanwarlal%20Sharma%2C%20was%20known%20for%20providing%20meals%20in%20the%20assembly%20during%20political%20standoffs.%20In%20previous%20instances%2C%20food%20had%20been%20arranged%20from%20Mr%20Sharma's%20home%20in%20similar%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20standoff%20was%20triggered%20after%20state%20minister%20Avinash%20Gehlot%20referred%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20as%20%26quot%3Baapki%20dadi%26quot%3B%20(your%20grandmother).%20Congress%20MLAs%20took%20strong%20objection%20to%20the%20statement%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20comments%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20assembly%20records.%20The%20situation%20escalated%20when%20multiple%20party%20leaders%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Tikaram%20Jully%2C%20staged%20an%20overnight%20protest%20inside%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jully%20called%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20minister's%20remarks.%20He%20accused%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20attempting%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20its%20own%20ministers'%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MLAs%20were%20ready%2C%20we%20had%20talked%20to%20the%20speaker%20but%20we%20did%20not%20get%20any%20reply%20from%20there.%20I%20also%20think%20that%20the%20government%20just%20wants%20to%20put%20out%20the%20message%20publicly%20that%20the%20Opposition%20is%20simply%20protesting%20and%20blocking%2C%20but%20there%20is%20nothing%20like%20that%20from%20our%20side.%20The%20Opposition%20is%20only%20asking%20that%20the%20remarks%20made%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ji%20be%20taken%20back%2C%20the%20way%20they%20are%20making%20an%20issue%20of%20it%20and%20covering%20up%20the%20mistakes%20of%20their%20(BJP)%20ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jully%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20today%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLAs%20argued%20that%20the%20Speaker%20could%20have%20resolved%20the%20issue%20by%20expunging%20the%20remarks