sider.com%2Fhail-stone-storm-damage-threat-to-american-homes-insurance-premiums-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740216182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b50f16eb4be2fff9a4f3ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhail-stone-storm-damage-threat-to-american-homes-insurance-premiums-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wildfires%20and%20hurricanes%20may%20grab%20headlines%2C%20but%20the%20looming%20risks%20of%20a%20lesser-known%20climate%20disaster%20%E2%80%94%20hail%20%E2%80%94%20are%20worrying%20homeowners%20and%20insurance%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dlatu%40insider.com%20(Dan%20Latu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhail-stone-storm-damage-threat-to-american-homes-insurance-premiums-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Royal%20Society%20Hasn't%20Done%20This%20In%20150%20Years.%20But%20May%20Do%20It%20To%20Elon%20Musk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20risks%20being%20expelled%20from%20the%20UK's%20oldest%20scientific%20academy%20-%20the%20Royal%20Society.%20The%20move%20comes%20after%20over%202%2C700%20scientists%20signed%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20world's%20richest%20man's%20membership%20in%20the%20esteemed%20institution.%20A%20meeting%20in%20this%20regard%20will%20take%20place%20on%20March%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20open%20letter%2C%20professor%20Stephen%20Curry%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Imperial%20College%20London%2C%20has%20criticised%20the%20society%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20silence%20and%20apparent%20inaction%26quot%3B%20regarding%20Musk's%202018%20fellowship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmstdn.social%2F%40StephenCurry%2F114025762348190105%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmstdn.social%2F%40StephenCurry%2F114025762348190