s%20because%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20involvement%20in%20the%20US%20administration.%20The%2053-year-old%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20advisor%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20also%20heads%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20members%2C%20including%20University%20of%20Oxford%20psychologist%20Professor%20Dorothy%20Bishop%2C%20have%20already%20resigned%20in%20protest.%C2%A0Professor%20Bishop%20had%20said%20she%20refused%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20an%20institution%20that%20calls%20Elon%20Musk%20a%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20more%20than%20150%20years%2C%20no%20member%20has%20been%20expelled%20from%20the%20Royal%20Society%20except%20Rudolf%20Eric%20Raspe%2C%20who%20was%20removed%20due%20to%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Royal%20Society%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Royal%20Society%2C%20founded%20in%201660%20in%20London%2C%20supports%20scientific%20research%2C%20provides%20scientific%20advice%20to%20policymakers%2C%20and%20fosters%20international%20and%20worldwide%20cooperation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20and%20engineers%20from%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20Commonwealth%20who%20have%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20the%20advancement%20of%20natural%20knowledge%2C%20such%20as%20mathematics%2C%20engineering%20science%2C%20and%20medical%20science%2C%20are%20among%20the%20society's%20core%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20honoured%20renowned%20members%20like%20Isaac%20Newton%2C%20Albert%20Einstein%2C%20Stephen%20Hawking%2C%20and%20Charles%20Darwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20president%20is%20Adrian%20Smith%2C%20who%20took%20over%20from%20Venki%20Ramakrishnan%20in%20November%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740216120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F0k678oo8_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_21_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froyal-society-elon-musk-