0arrested%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20home%20minister%2C%20Jawahar%20Singh%20Bedham%20said%20that%20Inspector%20General%20of%20jail%20Vikram%20Singh%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Dousa%20jail%2C%20a%20criminal%2C%20namely%20Rinku%2FRanwa%2C%20he%20is%20jailed%20in%20POCSO%20act.%20Through%20mobile%2C%20he%20called%20the%20control%20room%20yesterday%20and%20threatened%20to%20kill%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20home%20minister%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20took%20immediate%20action%20and%20arrested%20him.%20We%20gave%20direction%20to%20DG%20jail%20and%20DG%20jail%20gave%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20investigation%20to%20IG%20jail%20Vikram%20Singh...how%20did%20the%20criminal%20get%20a%20phone%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20jail%20authorities%20had%20carried%20out%20an%20inspection%20an%20hour%20before%20of%20the%20jail%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20further%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20another%20officer%20of%20the%20jail%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20the%20police%20is%20currently%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%20it%20looks%20like%20an%20officer%20inside%20the%20jail%20is%20also%20involved.%20We%20will%20take%20strict%20action%20so%20that%20such%20incidents%20don't%20happen%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Bedham%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20July%20of%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20CM%20received%20another%20death%20threat%20from%20the%20Shyalawas%20Jail%20in%20Dausa%2C%20with%20the%20police%20identifying%20the%20accused%20and%20recovering%20nine%20mobile%20phones%20from%20the%20jail%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(ASP)%20Lalsot%20Lokesh%20Sonwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDausa%20SP%20Ranjita%20Sharma%20received%20a%20ph