bhajanlal-sharma-gets-death-threat-from-man-in-jail-7768180%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWomen%20Of%20Delhi%20Cheated%26quot%3B%3A%20Atishi%20To%20Rekha%20Gupta%20Over%20%26quot%3BFailed%26quot%3B%20Promises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20today%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20newly%20sworn-in%20Chief%20Minister%20Rekha%20Gupta%2C%20questioning%20the%20BJP%20government's%20failure%20to%20pass%20a%20promised%20financial%20assistance%20scheme%20for%20women%20in%20its%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%2C%20Atishi%20sought%20time%20to%20meet%20Ms%20Gupta%20along%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20Legislature%20Party%20on%20Sunday%20to%20discuss%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20that%20would%20provide%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20women%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20heartiest%20congratulations%20to%20you%20on%20assuming%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20post%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi's%20letter%20reads.%20%26quot%3BBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%2C%20had%20promised%20the%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20Delhi%20in%20a%20rally%20organized%20on%20January%2031%2C%202025%2C%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%20that%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20a%20scheme%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20would%20be%20passed%20for%20them%20in%20the%20very%20first%20cabinet%20meeting.%20He%20said%20-%20this%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Delhi%20government%20held%20its%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20on%20February%2020%2C%20but%20the%20scheme%20was%20not%20passed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20Delhi%20had%20believed%20in%20Modi%20ji's%20guarantee%2C%20and%20now%20they%20feel%20cheated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20urged%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20AAP%20delegation%20on%20Sunday%20to%20address%20their%20concerns%20and%20take%20concrete%20action%20on%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%2C%20who%20won%20from%20the%20Kalkaji%20assembly%20constituency%20by%20beating%20the%20BJP's%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20in%20the%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20criticised%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20failing%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20electoral%20promises%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20yesterday%20as%20well.%20She%20said%20that%20before%20the%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20both%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20BJP%20national%20president%20JP%20Nadda%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20scheme%20would%20be%20approved%20in%20the%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20and%20that%20every%20eligible%20woman%20would%20receive%20Rs%202%2C500%20in%20her%20bank%20account%20by%20March%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisplaying%20campaign%20posters%20featuring%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Ms%20Gupta%2C%20Atishi%20challenged%20the%20BJP%20to%20clarify%20when%20the%20promised%20financial%20assistance%20would%20be%20deposited.%20%26quot%3BWas%20this%20just%20another%20election%20gimmick%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20financial%20support%20for%20women%20was%20central%20to%20the%20Delhi%20election%20campaign%2C%20with%20both%20AAP%20and%20BJP%20making%20competing%20promises.%20Following%20the%20election%20results%2C%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20ended%20AAP's%20reign%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20AAP%20has%20maintained%20pressure%20on%20the%20new%20administration%20to%20fulfil%20its%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20AAP%20was%20ousted%20from%20power%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%208%2C%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20met%20with%20the%2022%20newly%20elected%20AAP%20MLAs%20at%20his%20residence.%20Following%20the%20meeting%2C%20Atishi%20reiterated%