-7767406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Adam%20Schiff%2C%20Senator%20Whose%20Remark%20On%20Kash%20Patel%20Angered%20Elon%20Musk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Senator%20Adam%20Schiff%20was%20among%20the%20fiercest%20critics%20of%20Kash%20Patel's%20nomination%20as%20FBI%20director%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20hack%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bsycophant%26quot%3B%20unfit%20for%20the%20role.%20Despite%20strong%20opposition%20from%20Democrats%2C%20the%20Senate%20on%20Thursday%20confirmed%20Patel%20to%20lead%20the%20nation's%20top%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20agency.%20About%20half%20a%20dozen%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%20Democrats%20gathered%20outside%20FBI%20headquarters%20earlier%20that%20day%C2%A0in%20a%20final%20attempt%20to%20block%20his%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20someone%20we%20cannot%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schiff.senate.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fwatch-sen-schiff-speaks-out-against-kash-patels-nomination-as-fbi-director%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Senator%20Schiff%20of%20California.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20someone%20who%20lacks%20the%20character%20to%20do%20this%20job%2C%20someone%20who%20lacks%20the%20integrity%20to%20do%20this%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20Republicans%20knew%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20qualification%20Kash%20Patel%20has%20to%20be%20FBI%20director%20is%20that%20when%20everyone%20else%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20said%20'no%2C%20I%20won't%20do%20that%2C%20that%20crosses%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20legal%20lines%2C'%20Kash%20Patel%20said%20sign%20me%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Schiff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20Schiff's%20sharp%20criticism%20has%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20he%20may%20be%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Benemies%26quot%3B%20Kash%20Patel%20mentioned%20in%20his%202023%20book%20Government%20Gangsters.%20Mr%20Patel%2C%20did%20not%20hold%20back%20in%20his%20response%20to%20Mr%20Schiff's%20comments.%20%26quot%3BAdam%20Schiff%20is%20the%20worst%20criminal%20in%20Congress%20in%20the%20last%20250%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20echoed%20this%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BAdam%20Schiff%20is%20a%20criminal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAdam%20Schiff%20is%20a%20criminal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ff2tbVUcsXg%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ff2tbVUcsXg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1892638036547997925%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2020%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Adam%20Schiff%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20Schiff%20was%20born%20in%20Framingham%2C%20Massachusetts.%20He%20attended%20Monte%20Vista%20High%20School%20in%20Danville%2C%20California.%20Mr%20Schiff%20went%20on%20to%20study%20at%20Stanford%20University%20and%20later%20earned%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20Harvard%20Law%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20law%20school%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20work%20as%20a%20law%20clerk%20for%20Judge%20William%20Matthew%20Byrne%2C%20Jr.%20He%20later%20joined%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20as%20a%20federal%20prosecutor.%20During%20his%20six-year%20tenure%2C%20he%20prosecuted%20Richard%20Miller%2C%20the%20first%20FBI%20agent%20indicted%20for%20spying%20for%20Russia.%20He%20also%20established%20one%20of%20the%20first%20federal%20environmental%20crimes%20units%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Adam%20Schiff%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20California%20State%20Senate%20as%20its%20youngest%20member.%20During%20his%20term%2C%20he%20introduced%20the%20Schiff-Cardenas%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Crime%20Prevention%20Act%20of%202000%2C%20which%20funded%20programmes%20to%20keep%20at-risk%20youth%20out%20of%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20efforts%20to%20expand%20the%20Metro%20Gold%20Line%20earned%20him%20the%20nickname%20%26quot%3BFather%20of%20the%20Gold%20Line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20Adam%20Schiff%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20US%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20serving%20on%20key%20committees%2C%20including%20Judiciary%2C%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Intelligence%2C%20where%20he%20later%20became%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20the%20first%20impeachment%20inquiry%20against%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20was%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20Russia's%20election%20interference.%20He%20also%20pushed%20for%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20after%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20As%20House%20Intelligence%20Committee%20chair%2C%20he%20pushed%20for%20deeper%20probes%2C%20facing%20criticism%20from%20Republicans.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20House%20pushed%20to%20punish%20him%20for%20spreading%20what%20they%20called%20false%20claims%2C%20but%20he%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Adam%20Schiff%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20US%20Senate%2C%20representing%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Schiff%20was%20instrumental%20in%20getting%20Congress%20to%20formally%20recognise%20the%20Armenian%20Genocide%20in%202019.%20He%20championed%20the%20Protecting%20Our%20Democracy%20Act%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20prevent%20presidential%20abuse%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740200460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F0kca7hk_adam-schiff-elon-musk-_625x300_22_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-adam-schiff-senator-whose-remark-on-kash-patel-angered-elon-musk-7767201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Senator%20Adam%20Schiff%20was%20among%20the%20f