GC%20officials.%20Brigadier%20General%20Ali%20Fadavi%2C%20deputy%20commander%20of%20the%20IRGC%2C%20and%20Brigadier%20General%20Amir%20Ali%20Hajizadeh%2C%20commander%20of%20the%20IRGC's%20Aerospace%20Force%2C%20have%20also%20issued%20similar%20statements%20vowing%20to%20destroy%20Israel%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20True%20Promise%203%2C%20the%20planned%20third%20attack%20against%20Israel%20following%20Iranian%20strikes%20in%20April%20and%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heightened%20rhetoric%20has%20reportedly%20coincided%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20IRGC%20missile%20production.%20Iran%20recently%20received%20a%201%2C000-ton%20shipment%20of%20rocket%20fuel%20precursor%20chemicals%20from%20China%2C%20claimed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fmiddle-east%2Farticle-842197%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20IRGC%20unveiled%20a%20new%20underground%20%26quot%3Bmissile%20city%26quot%3B%2C%20%C2%A0an%20underground%20missile%20base%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20target%20destroyers%20in%20strategic%20southern%20waters%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jerusalem%20Post%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jpost.com%2Fisrael-news%2Farticle-843077%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eciting%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoon-to-be-published%20article%20in%20Middle%20East%20Quarterly%26quot%3B%20quotes%20Colin%20Winston%2C%20a%2030-year%20CIA%20veteran%20and%20former%20head%20of%20research%20at%20the%20American-Israel%20Public%20Affairs%20Committee%20(AIPAC)%20who%20argues%20that%20now%20is%20the%20optimal%20time%20for%20a%20joint%20US-Israeli%20strike%20on%20Iran's%20nuclear%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHezbollah%20and%20Hamas%20no%20longer%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Jerusalem%20Post%20quotes%20Mr%20Winston.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Islamic%20Republic%20o