%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20wins%20%E2%80%94%20in%202018%2C%20Chef%20Garima%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20chef%20to%20earn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357879%2Fmichelin-star-indian-restaurants-avatara-junoon-gaa-veeraswamy-gymkhana-rania-tamarind-semma-benares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20MICHELIN%20star%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%202019%20she%20was%20named%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20Best%20Female%20Chef%2C%20and%20in%202023%2C%20her%20restaurant%20Gaa%20won%20its%20second%20MICHELIN%20Star%20%E2%80%94%20have%20only%20furthered%20her%20drive%20to%20assure%20Indian%20cuisine%20its%20moment%20in%20the%20sun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Gaa%20experience%3A%20Where%20contemporary%20Indian%20flavours%20meet%20Thai%20ingredients%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20a%2060-year-old%20%3Cem%3Ebaan%20ruen%20thai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20Thai%20home)%2C%20in%20Bangkok%E2%80%99s%20Wattana%20area%2C%20Gaa%20plays%20host%20to%20a%20gastronomic%20delegation%20every%20day.%20The%20participants%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20sort%20you%E2%80%99d%20expect.%20Dressed%20in%20vibrant%20colours%2C%20and%20natives%20of%20different%20regions%20across%20Thai%20and%20Indian%20subcontinents%2C%20these%20herbs%2C%20spices%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Econdiments%2C%20and%20vegetables%20convene%20to%20lend%20their%20expertise%20to%20the%20dishes%20of%20the%20day%2C%20which%20lie%20at%20the%20confluence%20of%20Indian%20and%20Thai%20cultures.%20They%20mark%20a%20coming-together%20of%20flavours%2C%20textures%2C%20and%20ingredients%20inspired%20by%20the%20two%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cim