spectively%2C%20while%20precipitation%20decreased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20are%20significant.%20%E2%80%9CChinars%20are%20crucial%20for%20preventing%20soil%20erosion%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20environmentalist%20Raja%20Muzaffar%20Bhat.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20deep%20roots%20act%20as%20anchors%2C%20and%20they%20are%20vital%20carbon%20sinks.%20During%20the%202014%20floods%2C%20areas%20with%20chinar%20trees%20were%20significantly%20less%20affected%20by%20soil%20erosion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20tech%20to%20save%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20chinar%20trees%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%20decided%20to%20take%20an%20innovative%20step%20towards%20protecting%20these%20iconic%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20%E2%80%98aadhar%20identity%E2%80%99%20for%20every%20single%20chinar%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20valley.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20chinar%20trees%20are%20being%20geotagged%20with%20scannable%20QR%20plates%2C%20and%20are%20being%20monitored%20and%20safeguarded%20using%20cutting%20edge%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20ultrasonography-based%20(USG)%20gadgets%2C%20we%20can%20assess%20the%20health%20and%20risk%20levels%20of%20each%20chinar%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20evaluation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tariq%20explains.%20This%20technology%20allows%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20vulnerabilities%20and%20targeted%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%2C%20spearheading%20the%20campaign%2C%20is%20utilising%20a%20Geographical%20Information%20System%20(GIS)%20to%20create%20a%20comprehensive%20database.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20will%